name: Beauty 21 gift voucher - $100
description:
Treat your family or friends with a Beauty 21 gift voucher to the value of $100. The gift voucher can be redeemed for the following beauty services:

- facials & body treatments 
- paramedical skin solutions
- spa beauty treatments
- manicure & pedicure (including Shellac)
- massage
- waxing & electrolysis 
- instant spray tanning
- make-up styling

Alternatively, the gift voucher can be redeemed on product purchase from the following range:
- guinot
- MD Formulations
- Intraceuticals
- BIOLINE - JATO 
- Youngblood
- OPI
- Tuscan Tan

Visit www.beauty21.com.au for more information on all Beauty 21's products and services.

Terms and conditions
> Gift voucher is in Australian dollars (AUD)
> Gift voucher can be used towards any Beauty 21 services or products and is valid until the expiry date specified by Beauty 21.
> The expiry is 12 months from date of purchase. 
> Gift voucher is to the value nominated on the gift voucher and is not redeemable for cash or valid with any other offer.
> Full value of gift voucher is to be used in the one transaction.
> Gift voucher will be subject to verification at the time of purchase and Beauty 21 reserves the right to reject any gift vouchers
that have been or appear to have been forged or tampered with.
